# 🛒 Amazon Sales Analytics & Forecasting
Python • SQL • Power BI • Time-Series Modeling

## ✅ Project Overview  
An end-to-end analytics project designed to analyze Amazon sales performance, profitability, customer trends, and forecast future demand using time-series models. The system integrates Python, SQL and Power BI into a unified data pipeline.

---

## ✅ Architecture  
Python Cleaning → SQL Data Modeling → Power BI ETL → DAX KPIs → Forecasting (ARIMA/Prophet)

---

## ✅ Key Features  
- Data cleaning & preprocessing using Python (Pandas)  
- Fact–dimension SQL data model  
- Forecasting using ARIMA/Prophet (30‑day demand prediction)  
- Power BI dashboard for Sales, Profitability & Category insights  
- Anomaly detection using rolling averages & Z‑score  
- Automated refresh-ready BI pipeline  

---

## ✅ Tech Stack  
- Python (Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib)  
- SQL Server / MySQL  
- Power BI (DAX, data model, visuals)  
- Excel / CSV  

